    "name": "Mika and The Witch's Mountain",
    "steam_appid": 1819460,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1819460/extras/500fecc175babbd52eb7446138aa5a79.avif?t=1771579088\" width=600 height=150 /></span><br><br><strong>Mika and the Witch’s Mountain</strong>（米卡与魔女之山）讲述了一位颇有抱负的小魔女为岛民送包裹的奇幻冒险故事。 探索每一个角落和裂缝，乘坐魔法扫帚翱翔天空。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1819460/extras/178011f4c5335f9e5ee92f201bf40d29.poster.avif?t=1771579088\" width=600 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1819460/extras/178011f4c5335f9e5ee92f201bf40d29.webm?t=1771579088\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1819460/extras/178011f4c5335f9e5ee92f201bf40d29.mp4?t=1771579088\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>在这个关于努力、友谊和社区的故事中一路成长，并最终登上山顶；让我们的心自由飞翔。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1819460/extras/8bde6e7f702dab7ce60574c64c7e3fb0.avif?t=1771579088\" width=600 height=124 /></span><br><br>拿起你的魔法扫帚，发现隐藏在山中的所有秘密，同时了解风趣的山民。努力工作，获得一把足够好的魔法扫帚来实现你的目标：登上山顶。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1819460/extras/b8f629974db182ac438d11189928320e.poster.avif?t=1771579088\" width=600 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1819460/extras/b8f629974db182ac438d11189928320e.webm?t=1771579088\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1819460/extras/b8f629974db182ac438d11189928320e.mp4?t=1771579088\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>本游戏的核心是带给你愉悦满足的飞行感觉。米卡将在她的山顶之旅中翱翔天空，同时探索Gaun山的美丽风景。<br><br><strong>Mika</strong>将向岛上各地的村民送包裹，他们会对她的服务进行评价。这样她就可以赚钱来购买具有独特飞行能力的新扫帚。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1819460/extras/b7ed8c83914235bbeb73dfaf20d83352.webp?t=1771579088\" width=850 height=50 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>飞越美丽的岛屿。探索一个充满秘密和魔法的迷你开放世界。<br></li><li>在环岛飞行时保护包裹免受风吹雨打。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1819460/extras/a92438a0c15a4ead603d6eb187ce8c26.avif?t=1771579088\" width=600 height=134 /></span><br></li><li>扮演一个在小岛上送包裹的小魔女。<br></li><li>用不同的服装、路线、宝藏等来完善你的收藏。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1819460/extras/81e98bde9d4cc1b03cecb93c0b6f018a.avif?t=1771579088\" width=600 height=201 /></span><br></li><li>一个轻松暖心的故事，令人放松身心。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1819460/extras/6eaa4219cb2aef23e12f84cd55b23d55.avif?t=1771579088\" width=588 height=328 /></span>",
